item.title: Why we can't have nice things
item.description: You may be familiar with the name Taboola. They are a US-based advertising agency that became infamous for plastering the internet with “Recommended” links at the end of news articles and online content. You could lose belly fat by not eating one fruit. Or a politician was suggesting you buy gold.
